title: MUMBLE_GET_VOICE_CHANNEL_FROM_SERVER_ID
content:
0x221C09F1// MumbleGetVoiceChannelFromServerId
int MUMBLE_GET_VOICE_CHANNEL_FROM_SERVER_ID(int serverId);Parameters:serverId: The player's server id.Returns: Int representing the identifier of the voice channel.Returns the mumble voice channel from a player's server id.
